    GET  /api/admin/dashboard/alerts     (all actionable alerts, severity-sorted)
  System Config:
    GET  /api/admin/system-config
    POST /api/admin/system-config
    POST /api/admin/system-config/refresh
  User Management:
    POST /api/admin/users/bootstrap  (ADMIN_BOOTSTRAP_SECRET — first admin only)
