    POST /api/admin/users/demote     (requires existing admin)
    GET  /api/admin/users/:uid/claims
  Payments (Stripe):
    GET  /api/payments/publishable-key
    POST /api/payments/create-intent
    POST /api/payments/webhook
  Simulation API (v1):
    GET  /api/v1/health
    POST /api/v1/fx/quote                (lock quote, 90s TTL + 30s buffer)
    GET  /api/v1/fx/quotes
    POST /api/v1/wallet/topup
    GET  /api/v1/wallet/:userId
    POST /api/v1/remittance/initiate     (Idempotency-Key header | user-balance | liquidity | circuit-breaker)
    GET  /api/v1/remittance/:txId
    POST /api/v1/campaign/contribute     (AML compliance metadata required)
    POST /api/v1/recurring/process       (scheduleId-based idempotency)
    GET  /api/v1/liquidity               (auto-replenish enabled)
    GET  /api/v1/circuit-breaker/status
    POST /api/v1/circuit-breaker/trip/:provider  (stripe|chapa|telebirr)
    POST /api/v1/circuit-breaker/reset           (restore all to CLOSED)
    POST /api/v1/simulation/reset                (full state wipe; pass { seed: true } to pre-fund wallets)
    POST /api/v1/simulation/seed                 (pre-fund test wallets — idempotent)
    POST /api/v1/simulation/drain                (drain all provider pools → PENDING_LIQUIDITY test setup)
  RESTful Campaign API:
    POST /api/campaigns/:campaignId/contribute   (RESTful alias, campaignId in URL)
